Package: genomicSimulation
Version: 0.1-1
Title: Simulate Breeding Schemes Across SNP Markers
Authors@R: c(person("Kira", "Villiers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="kirav@protonmail.com"))
Description: Functions to simulate breeding programs on SNP markers, making simulated
 phased genotypes, and functions to calculate or perform selection based on GEBVs from
 provided effect values.
